author: Devan Cole, CNN
title: US will see 100,000 to 200,000 coronavirus deaths and millions of cases, Fauci predicts
description: The nation's top infectious disease expert predicted Sunday that the United States will eventually see between 100,000 and 200,000 deaths from the novel coronavirus, which has already claimed more than 2,000 American lives as cases surge across the nation.
